ewcommand\shiftedwhiterule[2]&#123;%\hbox to \linewidth&#123;\color&#123;white&#125;%\hskip#1\leaders\vrule height1pt\hfil&#125;
ointerlineskip\vskip#2&#125;\etocsetstyle&#123;subsubsection&#125;&#123;\etocskipfirstprefix&#125;&#123;\shiftedwhiterule&#123;\leftskip&#125;&#123;6pt&#125;&#125;&#123;\heiti ootnotesize\leftskip2.5cm\hangindent1cmightskip1cm
